metadata.name: Land #2
metadata.description:
World Of Mythesda is a beautiful, ever-evolving fantasy universe full of creatures and splendid biomes.

Thanks to its own land, your baby creatures ([https://opensea.io/fr/collection/world-of-mythesda](https://opensea.io/fr/collection/world-of-mythesda)) will grow up and evolve, to be ready to fight. You can find all kinds of biomes, from lush forests of Chupacabra to dragon flying mountains and everything in between.

Collecting these unique digital creatures and their matching land is an exciting journey that grants you access to the final splendid collection of the evolved creatures. Discover those splendid biomes and let your imagination run wild as you explore its many wonders!
